channel.title: Only Brother can Connect
channel.description:

I'm using http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,534143.0.html
LummyScape, can't find shit, hopefully someone can take a look..
Also, i've tried to search for Class131_Sub2_Sub7.aString5636 = ClientSettings.ip; and all that was there is that blank stuff after ClientSettings.ip;
If i put an ip in this is the error it gives me..
